description:
Software purpose-built for planning and building teams. All the tools you need to assess, compare, annotate and approve digital plans.


New
- Added support for reading 32-bit HEIC files
- Added support for a setting to enable conditional access support for web logins
Changes
- Changed "JPEG Files(%s)" to "JPEG Files (%s)" to fix missing space
- Changed to show a message when document compare regions are used on document types that can't be used with regions
- Changed to clear find results after a document is changed in Read Mode or Forms Mode
Fixes
- Fixed a DPI issue with the reply edit control size in comments
- Fixed document compare regions not working with read-only documents with "Read-only documents can be modified for Save As" disabled
- Fixed drawing issues with reply and edit cancel buttons in comments when changing DPI or resizing the comments panel
- Fixed PNG and PBM/PGM/PPM not working for the $doctemp$ script command
